Aim:
To check whether a year is a leap year.

Algorithm:
Start
Input year
If (year%400==0) or (year%4==0 and year%100!=0) → Leap year
Else → Not leap year
Stop

program:
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
    int year;
    cout<<"Enter a year: ";
    cin>>year;

    if((year % 400 == 0) || (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0))
        cout<<"Leap Year";
    else
        cout<<"Not a Leap Year";
    return 0;
}

Sample Output:
Enter a year: 2024
Leap Year

Result:The program was executed successfully
